    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Variegated marble, of various shades of red, pink, and purple on a white ground-mass, quarried in ancient times principally at Epirus in Turkey.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
